name: UniversityofIllinoisEvents
0:
”Alexa, start illinois plans.”
”Alexa, start illinois plans and give me today's events.”
”Alexa, open illinois plans and tell me the events for Sunday.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: illinois plans
des: This skill provides a straight forward, convenient means for University of Illinois students, faculty, and family members to get information on events going on around the area. Simply ask questions like "What are today's events" or "Are there any event's going on tomorrow?"
